name: Flight Rising Swipp and Baldwin Item Counts
description: The original version of this style (found here) hasn't been updated since March and had a few errors, so I took it upon myself to freshen it up. Let me know if you find anything I missed and I'll try to fix it. Best used alongside this style to highlight the Swipp and Baldwin items like you see in the screenshots.
additional_info:
12-17-18 Update
AAAAAAHH I have no idea how I missed adding the items for the Dusty Pauper Rags bundle but I did. They've been added now!

10-6-2018 Update
The updates start comin' and they don't stop comin'. Here's a small one that includes the item counts for the Glowing Mint Bow set for Baldwin.

10-03-2018 Update
Apologies again. My life has been eaten up by Stardew Valley and I missed the new Baldwin Vista being added. Here it is now! As an aside, for those of you worried about using Stylish due to it violating Chrome's store policy, this style and pretty much every other style on this site is fully compatible right out of the box with Stylus, an alternative 
to Stylish that does the same thing while not being turned off randomly by Chrome. Give it a try!

08-13-2018 Update
Sorry for the wait, I've been on vacation. But I'm back now with the items for the Quetzeel and Blotched Quetzeel!

05-25-2018 Update
You would not believe your eyes, but I've added the new items for the new Swipp Gene, Firefly! 

05-17-2018 Update
Added the items for the new Swipp familiars, the Vermilion and Longwing Epiptites.
 
04-12-2018 Update
Added the item counts for the new Swipp and Baldwin Kelpie Manes.
Fixed the item count on the Shadow Runestone and Light Runestone

01-23-2018 Update
Added the item counts for the new Baldwin Genes and apparel.

01-08-2018 Update
Added the item counts for the new Swipp trades and Baldwin recipes released with the familiar colouring contest results. Use them wisely.
